16 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
17 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 72 O.S. 2021, Section 63.18A, is
18 amended to read as follows:
19 Section 63.18A. The following positions and personnel at the
20 Oklahoma Department of Veterans Affairs shall be in the unclassified
21 civil service exempt as provided in the Oklahoma Personnel Act Civil
22 Service and Human Capital Modernization Act:
23 1. Physicians assistants;
24 2. Occupational therapists;
