1 3. Physical therapists;
2 4. Pharmacists;
3 5. Speech pathologists;
4 6. Nurse practitioners;
5 7. Physical therapy assistants;
6 8. Administrative Assistant to the Director;
7 9. Programs Administrators;
8 10. Administrators, Veterans Centers; and
9 11. Assistant Administrators, Veterans Centers.
10 SECTION 2. AMENDATORY 72 O.S. 2021, Section 64, is
11 amended to read as follows:
12 Section 64. The status of positions that have been exempted by
13 executive order and positions previously authorized to be in the
14 unclassified service exempt from civil service rules are not
15 affected by this act.
16 SECTION 3. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
